How to check mn EC:
q_res = make_quartic(mn, quad_xy)
e_res = model_quartic_as_elliptic_curve(q_res[2], k0)
search_small_EC_points(e_res, q_res[2], k0, mn, quad_xy, 5, verbose=True)

How to check uv EC:
v_list = find_uv_by_EC(u, v0, 5, verbose=True)
solve_v_list(u, v_list)
